# Swiggy Clone
---
## Running the app

### To run the deployed app visit -  https://swiggy-clone-rho-azure.vercel.app/

To run the app locally, 

1.  download the repository in your pc locally.
2.  run these commands
    ### `npm install`
    ### `npm start`
